title: ‘Oumuamua II: Revenge of the First Messenger
itunes:title: ‘Oumuamua II: Revenge of the First Messenger
description:
Everyone’s favorite interstellar travel has been back in the news, thanks to curious speed increases and an intriguing paper on the possibility of alien solar sail technology. So join Robert Lamb and Joe McCormick as they dock once more with ‘Oumuamua as it tumbles out of our solar system.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
